
Overview of noun spoon

The noun spoon has 3 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                          
1. (1) spoon -- (a piece of cutlery with a shallow bowl-shaped container and a handle; used to stir or serve or take up food)
2. spoon, spoonful -- (as much as a spoon will hold; "he added two spoons of sugar")
3. spoon -- (formerly a golfing wood with an elevated face)

